PrecisOrder requiring the CANADIAN RADIO-TELEVISION AND TELECOMMUNICATIONS COMMISSION to report to the Governor in Council, at least once a year, on complaints received from individuals and small business customners regarding services provided by telecommunications service providers, and to submit its first report no later than April 6, 2008.
